âš™ï¸ Synchronized vs Non-Synchronized
HashMap is not synchronized.
Use Collections.synchronizedMap(map) for thread safety.
Or use ConcurrentHashMap in multithreading scenarios.

ğŸ’¡ Use Cases
Caching
Counting frequencies
Storing key-value config (e.g., environment variables)
Indexing by ID or name

ğŸ”’ Important Notes
Keys must be unique
Allows null key and values
Not thread-safe by default
Load factor and resizing affect performance

